      .a-fighters__text
        A-FIGHTERS was a comic I made during high school. A few years ago, when my MacBook harddrive crashed on me, I thought the work was lost forever. But fate would have it that I rediscover it in my Gmail archive.

      .a-fighters__text Untouched since 2009, A-FIGHTERS in all its glory returns to the internet once more.

      .a-fighters__text.chinese
        「甲級爭取者」是我於高中時期創作的一部漫畫。幾年前，因電腦不幸壞了，讓我以為此作品會永遠消失......但命運使我在郵件箱紀錄中尋回之。

      .a-fighters__text.chinese
        藝術復活, 原作2009版本回到互聯網，「甲級爭取者」現光榮回歸！

